N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 182.33 - Speed contests and races

State Regulations

Races or contests for speed are prohibited within the
parkway system and no person shall engage in or aid or abet in any motor
vehicle speed contest or exhibition of speed within the parkway
system. Notes
